text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_BattleDomeSign {
	"This is the BATTLE DOME!
	Your path to the invincible superstar!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_BattleFactorySign {
	"This is the BATTLE FACTORY!
	Seek out the toughest POKéMON!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_BattlePikeSign {
	"This is the BATTLE PIKE!
	Choose one of three paths!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_ThisIsBattleTower {
	"This is the BATTLE TOWER.

	TRAINERS bring their best-raised
	POKéMON for elimination-style matches."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_MayISeeYourTicket {
	"Hello, are you here for the ferry?
	May I see your TICKET?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_MustHaveTicketToBoard {
	"{PLAYER} doesn't have the TICKET…

	I'm terribly sorry.

	You must have a TICKET to board
	the ferry."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_WhereWouldYouLikeToGo {
	"{PLAYER} flashed the TICKET.

	Perfect! That's all you need!

	And where would you like to go?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_SlateportItIs {
	"SLATEPORT CITY it is, then!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_LilycoveItIs {
	"LILYCOVE CITY it is, then!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_SailWithUsAnotherTime {
	"Please sail with us another time!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_PleaseBoardFerry {
	"Please board the ferry and wait for
	departure."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_ThenWhereWouldYouLikeToGo {
	"Then, where would you like to go?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_BestOutOfAllMyFriends {
	"I'm the best out of all my friends.
	But here…
	I've been useless!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_CantFindBattleTower {
	"I want to go to the BATTLE TOWER,
	but I can't find it even though I have
	a map of the BATTLE FRONTIER.

	This place is just too big!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_GotSeasickOnWayHere {
	"I wanted to take a challenge as soon
	as I arrived here.

	But on the way, I got seasick…
	Urrrrp…"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_OnlyToughTrainersBroughtHere {
	"It's not as if just anyone can come
	here, you know?

	Only those TRAINERS who've been
	recognized as tough are brought here.

	That's why many TRAINERS don't even
	know about the BATTLE FRONTIER."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_SureWeCanChallengeWithNoMons {
	"Hey, bro…

	Are you sure we can make challenges
	even if we don't have any POKéMON?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_BigGuySaidIllLendYouMons {
	"Uh…
	I'm sure it'll be okay.

	I think…

	But remember that big scary guy?
	He said, “I'll lend you POKéMON!”"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_WhosRaisingThoseRentalMons {
	"That's the BATTLE FACTORY.
	You can rent strong POKéMON there.

	But it makes me wonder.
	Who's raising those rental POKéMON?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_ScaredOfPikeBecauseSeviper {
	"I'm scared of going into the BATTLE
	PIKE because of SEVIPER…

	B-but I came all the way here, so I will
	try to conquer everything!
	…Shudder…"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_LetsPlayRockPaperScissors {
	"Let's play rock, paper, scissors!
	One, two, three!

	… … … … … …"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_WonIllTakePikeChallenge {
	"Yay! I won!
	I will take the BATTLE PIKE challenge!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_LostIllPutOffPikeChallenge {
	"Oh, no…
	I lost.

	I guess I'm not very lucky today.
	I'll put off my BATTLE PIKE challenge
	until tomorrow."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_ChooseFishingOverBattling {
	"I believe I'm the only person here who,
	for some unknown reason, would choose
	fishing over battling.

	Huh? You can't catch anything here?
	That's disappointing…"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_KeepBattlingUntilIGetSymbol {
	"Today, I'm going to keep battling, no
	matter what, until I get a Symbol."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_YoureOffToChallengeDome {
	"Oh? You're off to challenge
	the BATTLE DOME?

	I'll wish you the best of luck.
	Let us both win our way up and meet
	in challenges."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_DomeIsHereGrandpa {
	"Grandpa, over here!
	The BATTLE DOME is here!
	Go get 'em, Grandpa!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_WontLetGentlemenBeatMe {
	"Ah, so this here is the BATTLE DOME?
	I won't let GENTLEMEN beat me!

	But where is the entrance?"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_NothingHereNotLongAgo {
	"There used to be nothing here not all
	that long ago.

	But, now look at this place! Amazing!
	I'll bring my mother out to see this."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_FinallyArrivedAtFrontier {
	"I've finally arrived at the BATTLE
	FRONTIER!

	I'm sure to grab attention with
	my looks and ability!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_SquareFilledWithToughPeople {
	"Munch, munch…

	It looks like this square's filled with
	tough people.

	Munch, munch…"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_MetOlderGirlAtPike {
	"Crunch, munch…

	A while back, I met this older girl
	at the BATTLE PIKE.

	She had these eyes that were scary
	in a real ornery way.

	Crunch, munch…

	She got all furious: “Will you quit
	eating!” Then she whaled on me.

	It was a hair-raising kind of
	scary experience, sure enough.

	Crunch, munch…"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_LastTimeOurEyesMet {
	"Huh? Will you listen to yourself?
	That's nothing!

	Why, the last time I cheered for him,
	our eyes met and sparks flew!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_DomeAceLookedBecauseOfMyCheering {
	"Whaaaaaat?!
	Pfft!

	That only happened because
	I happened to be sitting next to you!

	The DOME ACE only looked our way
	because my cheering was so loud!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_DomeAceIsMine {
	"Oh, shush!
	Keep that racket down!

	You fair-weather fans should stick
	to cheering for some GYM LEADER!

	The DOME ACE is mine!
	The only idol for me!"
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_FansOverThereUsedToBeTrainers {
	"Those people squabbling over there…

	It's hard to believe, but they once
	were TRAINERS, and good ones, too.

	They used to be incredibly tough,
	and they were famous, too.

	But they were obliterated by this
	certain TRAINER at a tournament.

	They were so thoroughly whipped,
	they became smitten by the TRAINER.

	Now they're just fans of the TRAINER.
	They go cheer for their idol at the
	BATTLE DOME every day now."
}

text BattleFrontier_OutsideWest_Text_MonWithLongTailInFrontier {
	"I heard a rumor that someone saw
	a POKéMON with an unusually long tail
	somewhere in the BATTLE FRONTIER.

	It must be adorable. I'm sure of it…

	Oh, challenges can wait. I feel driven
	to find the delightful creature!"
}
